org.apache.poi.util

Class NullLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.poi.util.NullLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    POILogger 

    @Internal
public class NullLogger
extends java.lang.Object
implements POILogger
    An empty-implementation of the POILogger. This can be used to not log anything, however the suggested approach in production systems is to use the CommonsLogger and configure proper log-handling via Apache Commons Logging.
